Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.060 --> 00:00:10.780
Suppose we physicists didn't tell anyone
how and why the laws of physics work.

00:00:10.780 --> 00:00:18.480
We just performed them and we said
it's because we have powers.

00:00:18.520 --> 00:00:25.280
If we did that, we would be running the world. People would be genuflecting as they

00:00:25.280 --> 00:00:30.140
walk by us. People would be bringing us
chickens from their farms. People would be

00:00:30.140 --> 00:00:36.180
begging that we don't incinerate them
with our antimatter device. The fact is

00:00:36.180 --> 00:00:42.180
the people who are doing the research
into magnetism, electromagnetism, more

00:00:42.180 --> 00:00:50.399
broadly... they tended to be educators,
academicians, not charlatans. And so only

00:00:50.399 --> 00:00:54.750
if your charlatan will you not tell
someone how something works, pretend you

00:00:54.750 --> 00:00:58.649
have the power and then you have the
power over that person. That is

00:00:58.649 --> 00:01:06.030
diabolical so it is incumbent upon the
educated educators class, if you can call

00:01:06.030 --> 00:01:11.100
it that, to say exactly what it is we're
doing and why and then it's not

00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:16.740
mysterious. You could do it too. You could
be a physicist. You could probe the

00:01:16.740 --> 00:01:24.780
operations of nature as we do. I have
powers and you don't, but I explain

00:01:24.780 --> 00:01:29.850
them and therefore you don't come
running to me thinking I'm your your

00:01:29.850 --> 00:01:34.560
demigod for having these powers. You say
what book did you learn this out of I

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:39.630
want to be able to do that too. So yeah
that we could have been magicians or

00:01:39.630 --> 00:01:45.000
charlatans. That's an education
issue right there and rather than beat

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:47.939
adults over the head because it's not
their fault they weren't educated or

00:01:47.939 --> 00:01:52.829
wasn't exposed or whatever, I think we
just have to rethink K through 12 and what is

00:01:52.829 --> 00:01:59.219
taught - what science is how, and why it
works. For me, science is vaccine against

00:01:59.219 --> 00:02:04.860
charlatans. It enables you to know
when someone is full of shit and when

00:02:04.860 --> 00:02:09.209
they're not. And that's power.
It's power of protection for yourself so

00:02:09.209 --> 00:02:13.740
you will not be exploited by those who
do not have your best interests in mind.

